title: Stanislav Mareyev
text:
Stanislav Igorevich Mareyev (; born 25 June 1996) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Irtysh%20Omsk">FC Irtysh Omsk</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Irtysh%20Omsk">FC Irtysh Omsk</a> on 1 August 2020 in a game against <a href="FC%20Yenisey%20Krasnoyarsk">FC Yenisey Krasnoyarsk</a>, as a starter.
